Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無限的時間將跳動停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.93,0:00:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人們悄聲無息地燃燒著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:09.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有任何人注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界已經脫軌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.73,0:00:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被紅世之火所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------OP-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:22.21,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}高鳴る鼓動　触れあう今世選んで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:29.35,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}進め　時の果てへ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:35.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ぽつり虚空の夜につぶやいた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:41.88,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「また明日ね」って言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:48.30,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}燃え巡り照らす太陽のような
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:54.66,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}強さと永遠に焦がれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:01:01.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}たったひとつ残せるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:08.18,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}存在を抱いた　この瞬間の笑顔を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:17.05,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ただひとつ守るべきは　君の未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:23.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}刹那  揺れて軋むこの世を選んで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:30.42,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ずっと運命の地を翔る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:36.84,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生え始めた炎　胸に秘め
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:44.51,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}今世を　来世を　君へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:22.21,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心潮湧動  循著切身之現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:29.35,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}向時間盡頭出發
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.35,0:00:35.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在靜默虛空的夜晚獨自言語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:41.88,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}明天還要再見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:48.30,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如同炙熱燃燒的太陽般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:54.66,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}強大得永遠灼燒著自我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.66,0:01:01.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如果只能留下唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:08.18,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我只想要你抱緊我  這瞬間的笑顏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:17.05,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}唯一值得守護的  只有你的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:23.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剎那  我選擇了這搖搖欲墜的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.84,0:01:30.42,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}永遠翱翔於那命運之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:36.84,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}內心偷偷萌生出的  這微弱火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.84,0:01:44.51,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}無論現在還是未來  飛往你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,---------------------------ED-----------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:23:00.43,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}目を閉じて　感じる鼓動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:05.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}もがいてる霧の中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:12.42,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}自分の場所　探している
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:16.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}闇雲に今日もずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:25.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}痛みのない世界なんてないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:36.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ触れたい　守りたいだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:46.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}紅く染まる夕暮れを　見つめる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:50.57,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Just look how beautiful is world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:24:01.74,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}この出会いで　違う自分見つけたから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:15.35,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}新しい明日を迎えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:23:00.43,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}閉上雙眼  感受心的跳動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.43,0:23:05.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在霧中掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.35,0:23:12.42,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}找尋著自我的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.42,0:23:16.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}如今仍然迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:25.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沒有苦痛的世界並不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.79,0:23:36.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}只想觸碰  守護而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:46.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}凝望被染紅的黃昏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:50.57,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}這個世界是多麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:24:01.74,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}因為在這場邂逅中  找到了不一樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.74,0:24:15.35,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}迎接新的明天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:49.89,Optitle,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(315,240)}在戰鬥之中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小緣你也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命是與紅世之徒戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這世界真正的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要修復這城市的歪曲看來需要你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.35,0:02:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.85,0:03:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪裘莉小姐所說的密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悼詞朗誦者的助手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  田中也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:13.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.96,0:03:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這應該是我說的話才對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然是密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.70,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的坂井悠二呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井悠二…已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.64,0:03:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…意外的很堅強呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般不會用這種口氣說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是擔心被大家知道了該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算剛才也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  必須去找吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:50.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的事被她知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.04,0:03:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後受了很大的打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得趕快解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算解釋也沒什麼意義了…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:01.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事實終歸是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米諾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:17.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌的聖廟差不多到了完成階段了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  教授
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像火霧戰士們完全不明白那到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…看來那個的目的並不是擴大歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會出現歪曲也許是其他計劃的副作用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…因為「探耽求究」是個喜歡做無用功的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微去看下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:05:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  到底想讓我做這種無聊的事到何時啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟作和榮太還沒到玻璃壇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍舊沒有那痴呆教授的氣息啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.28,0:05:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明派出那麼多磷子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來還有另一個火霧戰士在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.89,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道和探耽求究有沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接去問不是更快些嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去問問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.55,0:05:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.20,0:05:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和這些磷子的力量不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪裘莉說過又進來了一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個…是這個的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個讓吉田同學看到了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了…我也必須快點去玻璃壇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙是…火炬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小緣是火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…在這城市所發生的事情和坂井同學的事全都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都知道了卻還…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻還喜歡坂井同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經能一個人跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…原來是悼詞朗誦者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才在戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得感到一股子粗暴的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什麼啊…這不是老爺子們嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能鬆口氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.39,0:07:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎和神經病教授沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你們也對感覺不到探耽求究的氣息抱有疑問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.92,0:07:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然囉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底設置了什麼機關
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也想知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…那個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不是  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來怎麼一副死樣子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.57,0:07:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:08:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…這麼說來你就是坂井悠二吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…沒想到居然是密斯提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了對不起那小姑娘的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼把她捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為很適合作我們的協助者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適合？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.04,0:08:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了這種隨便的理由就把這個給她了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.03,0:08:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道突然看到了那些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.06,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會受到多麼大的打擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學明明什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.10,0:08:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼一定要拖她來我們的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.28,0:08:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎對你來說是相當重要的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學是個溫柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個不可以來我們世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該一直待在原來的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經身處無法回來的地方了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.00,0:09:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉…把你捲進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.68,0:09:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然畫面不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但首先得看清現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…對對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那個自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.25,0:09:43.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對它的實體稍微有些眉目了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:10:00.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和吉田一美那種人沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點也不像夏娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.75,0:10:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會說那種話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個自在式的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是利用城市的歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在空間裡挖洞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空間裡挖洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬把拼板的其中一塊拆下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說的話就容易理解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既明白又不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.61,0:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做這種事到底有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…探耽求究從很早以前就經常做莫名其妙的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.95,0:10:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  確實對城市有著影響
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以馬上開始調律才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像昨天和你說明的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能協助我們進行調律嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.29,0:10:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說協助？繼續將吉田同學捲進來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放著不管的話  城市會變得更加亂七八糟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.48,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和卡姆辛先生約定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.57,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且已經不要緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很對不起剛才逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.06,0:11:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「卡迪修的心室」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  什麼也沒發生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…好像稍微有點問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…因為那個自在式的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.93,0:11:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市裡標下的印記不能動了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說不能進行調律了的意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.41,0:11:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大姐  聽得到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.14,0:11:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  因為發生了很多事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦  玻璃壇啟動了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請…請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.88,0:12:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.24,0:12:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市上空的自在式某處有個洞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:16.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.85,0:12:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城市中到處瀰漫了的自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:23.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集中到了一處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在河上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.21,0:12:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概在祭典主會場附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說自在式的中心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.84,0:12:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在祭典主會場的河邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是塔台那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼都感覺不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來探耽求究把大部分是機器做成的磷子當作助手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.63,0:12:51.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是「助人為樂」多米諾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.54,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…本該想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.05,0:12:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那東西的話感覺不到氣息也很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒那個磷子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自在式也能破解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿著這個  聯絡用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防萬一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.60,0:13:05.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  馬爾克希亞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:10.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.17,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.71,0:13:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平時的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:17.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會說  一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教授
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.61,0:13:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混沌的聖廟前言的數字控制在預計範圍之內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來所接受委託的實驗就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出色
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼接下來就準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我所帶來樣品自在式進行預備實驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…火霧戰士接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那裡就自己想辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先前往集中點了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.76,0:13:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通信結束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  別突然動手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.70,0:14:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.27,0:14:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.77,0:14:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布有歪曲存在之力的防禦自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼呼呼…你們的攻擊是無效的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始變形
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.23,0:14:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…有什麼意義嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.34,0:14:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天曉得…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.82,0:14:45.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  剛才的機關確實挺麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太危險了無法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.08,0:14:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神經病教授
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.14,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城市外面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:57.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…看來沒打算躲起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:15:00.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得感覺不到氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…但準備從哪裡進來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然很明顯地在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  要上囉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飛艇？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探耽求究做事總是毫無意義的誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.32,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算這個作戰本身毫無意義也不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.91,0:15:43.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.45,0:15:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.52,0:15:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特地從空中來是有意義的也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.42,0:15:53.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才說過那裡的空間有一塊拼板被拆掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.82,0:15:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那飛艇也許是最後的拼板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.87,0:16:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小男孩的說法也有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起那機器人  去擾亂那空間不是更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.05,0:16:12.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正飛艇也有同樣的機關啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算攻擊也沒效的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  萬一真是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製造出那空間的自在法也會受到影響的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要接近那空間的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:25.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要解開自在式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.04,0:16:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…還有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼意外的話我會一起行動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話真想拒絕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽不到悠二的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二…好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.19,0:16:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  變形完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  火霧戰士們放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.88,0:17:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這才是高潮和華麗的最後一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實驗開始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自在法解除
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前往Van  Berry的街角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘著馬兒去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管到哪都有伴奏  嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火霧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是老樣子在發神經呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會讓你再隨心所欲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.34,0:17:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妨礙我探究神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這幫思考停滯的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多米諾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓他們瞧瞧珍藏已久的必殺技
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:16.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又變得奇怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對只是想這麼做而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這簡直可以稱為「雙保險」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請避開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會儘快擊落它的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？要動手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子要發飆了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.86,0:18:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.49,0:18:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快離開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不戰鬥就大勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合不合體根本沒什麼意義嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:24.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有意義是由我來決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是來幹什麼的…那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都不想知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:38.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.43,0:19:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉田同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學…是這麼溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經治不好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.39,0:19:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…真正的我已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.66,0:20:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在的我不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類？我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為身體和心都是這麼的溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡這樣的坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:55.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼…發動「卡迪修的心室」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐  請想像你城市的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.63,0:21:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據這個來糾正歪曲  進行調律
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.93,0:21:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:27.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從出生以來一直居住的這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.24,0:21:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是個溫暖的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.06,0:21:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坂井同學是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.98,0:21:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二他…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠二他不會和我一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.88,0:22:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威爾艾米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.00,0:22:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說有些做得過分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.35,0:22:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,探耽求究
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的工作可是事先準備而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實驗本身已經成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.17,0:22:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可沒資格發牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.67,0:22:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實  一定會順利進行的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.84,0:24:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與懷念的威爾艾米娜重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她卻敏感地察覺到了夏娜的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.66,0:24:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後她逼著夏娜做出了一個決定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.78,0:24:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  無情的威爾艾米娜
